com.sencha.gxt.theme.base.client.frame
Interface Frame

All Known Subinterfaces:
CollapsibleFrame
All Known Implementing Classes:
DivFrame, NestedDivFrame, TableFrame
public interface Frame

Defines the interface for classes which "frame" a given element and support both a header and content section. In general, frames provide support for rounded corners.

See Also:
TableFrame, DivFrame
